02:14.218 --> 02:16.261
Agh! Ooh!

02:38.700 --> 02:40.744
Ooh.

02:41.203 --> 02:42.371
Eee...

02:45.457 --> 02:47.501
Ah!

02:48.710 --> 02:50.754
Oh!

02:54.508 --> 02:56.552
(squawking )

03:00.389 --> 03:02.432
Holy jeez!

03:02.599 --> 03:07.646
Lookee what we got here.
That silly penguin is back again.

03:07.813 --> 03:11.400
No, Mr Madison, there no penguin.
You got too much sun today.

03:11.567 --> 03:14.361
- There no penguin!
- (squawks )

03:14.486 --> 03:19.199
It's too damn hot for a penguin
to be just walkin' around here.

03:20.868 --> 03:24.037
I gotta send him back to the South Pole.

03:25.789 --> 03:27.833
No!

03:36.884 --> 03:41.180
Penguin! Don't you dare run away!

03:42.347 --> 03:45.184
Come here, Mr Penguin!

03:46.602 --> 03:48.729
I'm one of the good guys, penguin.

03:48.854 --> 03:51.857
Don't run! Oh. Oh...

04:02.659 --> 04:05.204
Don't run!

04:05.329 --> 04:08.165
Don't run from me!

04:08.332 --> 04:10.375
Penguin!

04:14.963 --> 04:15.881
Penguin.

04:22.679 --> 04:25.599
You're a bad penguin.

04:26.183 --> 04:27.726
Whee-hee!

04:27.851 --> 04:29.728
Call the zoo!

04:33.315 --> 04:38.195
All the people at the zoo
are very nice, penguin.

04:38.320 --> 04:41.823
They'll treat you real respectable, like.

04:43.242 --> 04:46.411
There's nothing to worry about, big fella.

04:48.330 --> 04:50.207
Here I come!

04:58.131 --> 05:02.261
Right this way, gentlemen.
Mr Madison is expecting you.

05:06.014 --> 05:07.474
