06:52.621 --> 06:54.665
Stop looking at me, swan.

07:06.051 --> 07:08.220
(slurps )

07:20.107 --> 07:22.442
- Hey, Carl, what's up?
- Nothing much, Billy.

07:22.609 --> 07:24.945
- I see you got a little sun today.
- You think so?

07:25.112 --> 07:29.950
- I fell asleep by the pool for a few hours.
- Did you fall asleep or did you pass out?

07:31.952 --> 07:34.204
Shut up!

07:34.371 --> 07:38.834
That's enough, Billy. Because you took
your sweet-ass time coming down here,...

07:38.959 --> 07:41.170
..these gentlemen will miss their flights.

07:41.336 --> 07:45.174
Well, this guy can stay in my room,
I'll tell you that much.

07:51.972 --> 07:54.349
Billy? Eat your soup.

07:55.058 --> 07:56.768
It's good soup.

07:58.145 --> 08:01.315
Gentlemen, I can't thank you enough
for coming this evening.

08:01.481 --> 08:03.901
(yells gibberish )

08:04.067 --> 08:07.404
Please, Billy, please,
no gibberish tonight, please. I beg you.

08:07.571 --> 08:09.573
Sorry, Daddy.

08:10.407 --> 08:14.536
This is a big night for me tonight, gents.
I have an important announcement.

08:14.703 --> 08:16.955
(fast gibberish )

08:17.122 --> 08:20.209
That's it, Billy! Get the hell outta here!

08:22.461 --> 08:24.755
(slow gibberish )

08:33.013 --> 08:36.975
- Nice talkin' to you, Billy.
- (singsong gibberish )

08:38.101 --> 08:39.937
(yells )

08:49.446 --> 08:51.448
Right. One, two, three!

08:54.076 --> 08:56.995
Hey, Billy, how come
you ain't poundin' any tonight?

08:57.120 --> 09:01.416
I don't know. My dad was yellin' at me.
I'm just not in the mood.

09:02.876 --> 09:08.549
Hey, Billy, who would you rather bone,
Meg Ryan or Jack Nicholson?

09:08.715 --> 09:12.511
