has the hotel operator speaking gibberish?

10:06.315 --> 10:08.192
Oh, Billy, Billy boy.

10:08.358 --> 10:12.070
When are you gonna find
whatever it is you're lookin' for?

10:12.237 --> 10:14.656
Here's a nice piece of shit.

10:20.787 --> 10:24.666
My, oh, my. Wait till old man Clemens
realises it's a bag of shit.

10:24.833 --> 10:27.878
He's gonna shit when he realises it's shit.

10:28.045 --> 10:30.589
Who got the lighter?

10:30.756 --> 10:32.758
Come on.

10:41.266 --> 10:43.268
Light it.

10:47.648 --> 10:49.650
(rings doorbell)

10:52.194 --> 10:54.696
