32:03.131 --> 32:07.386
OK, so let's all open up
our Reading is Fun books to page 69.

32:07.511 --> 32:09.555
69!

32:12.266 --> 32:15.102
Class, say hello to Billy Madison.

32:15.227 --> 32:18.564
Hello, Billy Madison.

32:18.689 --> 32:21.608
