35:11.069 --> 35:13.113
Z... Z...

35:22.122 --> 35:23.749
Rirruto?

35:24.833 --> 35:27.127
Those are Zs.

35:27.252 --> 35:29.171
They look like Rs to me.

35:29.296 --> 35:34.635
That's not fair! Rizzuto is not a word.
He's a baseball player. You're cheating.

35:34.760 --> 35:37.137
Would you like to try the word ''buzz''?

35:37.262 --> 35:39.264
(children laugh )

35:39.389 --> 35:42.226
I hate cursive and I hate all of you!

35:42.351 --> 35:44.853
I'm never comin' back to school! Never!

35:44.978 --> 35:47.272
(children laugh )

35:51.401 --> 35:53.445
(Juanita ) Billy!

36:02.037 --> 36:04.206
I swear, I'm sick. I can't go to school.

36:04.331 --> 36:08.836
