on my living-room floor.

1:04:22.988 --> 1:04:27.367
- Come on, Billy, you know that...
- Talky, talky, talky.

1:04:27.493 --> 1:04:29.620
No more talky.

1:04:29.745 --> 1:04:32.206
You got a lighter in here?

1:04:35.209 --> 1:04:37.294
Oh.

1:04:37.419 --> 1:04:40.214
I see what's goin' on in here.

1:04:43.550 --> 1:04:47.137
So sorry to interrupt!

1:04:52.267 --> 1:04:54.311
Proceed.

1:04:55.604 --> 1:04:58.065
Billy, you're losing your mind.

1:05:01.693 --> 1:05:03.904
All right, boys' night out!

1:05:04.071 --> 1:05:05.572
Let's go!

1:05:11.578 --> 1:05:13.622
(snoring )

1:05:30.347 --> 1:05:32.891
Ow!

1:05:33.433 --> 1:05:35.894
I need to talk to you.

1:05:46.363 --> 1:05:48.407
Jeez!

1:05:49.283 --> 1:05:51.743
What's goin' on, man?

1:05:54.079 --> 1:05:59.585
I think Billy and his girlfriend
are playin' water polo or somethin'.

1:06:01.295 --> 1:06:04.089
Hey, maybe they're playin' Marco Polo.

1:06:04.882 --> 1:06:06.800
Marco.

1:06:08.135 --> 1:06:10.554
- Jeez, that was a great game.
- Yeah.

1:06:15.934 --> 1:06:19.354
I got an idea for you.
Instead of being an idiot every day,...

1:06:19.480 --> 1:06:22.816
..why don't you go back to school,
graduate and get the company?

1:06:22.941 --> 1:06:25.152
Cos I don't want it any more.

1:06:25.903 --> 1:06:30.199
- What do you mean, you don't want it?
- I got somethin' comin' outta my nose?

1:06:30.324 --> 1:06:33.368
I can't believe I liked someone
who could roll over and die.

1:06:33.494 --> 1:06:38.373
I ain't rollin' over and dyin'. I was set up.
And, worst of all, nobody believes me.

1:06:38.499 --> 1:06:42.044
I believe you, Billy. And I believe in you.

1:06:42.169 --> 1:06:45.881
You know, some people have no willpower,
no brains, no vision.

1:06:46.006 --> 1:06:48.675
They just drift through life
like lumps of crap.

1:06:48.800 --> 1:06:51.178
What is she talkin' about?

1:06:51.303 --> 1:06:55.265
And you have all those things.
You're just afraid to use 'em.

1:06:55.390 --> 1:07:00.312
Don't be. You say you're not a loser,
Billy Madison. So win.

1:07:16.370 --> 1:07:19.206
~ Yes, I will go back to school

1:07:19.331 --> 1:07:22.459
~ And achieve victory

1:07:22.584 --> 1:07:25.587
~ No man will take
what my father has built

1:07:25.712 --> 1:07:30.217
~ Unless that man is me

1:07:30.342 --> 1:07:33.554
~ My Billy, sweet Billy boy

1:07:33.679 --> 1:07:36.140
~ I knew you would go back

1:07:36.807 --> 1:07:39.935
~ No one can stop you if you try

1:07:40.060 --> 1:07:42.271
~ Don't I have a nice rack?

1:07:46.191 --> 1:07:49.069
~ Veronica, I thank you

1:07:49.194 --> 1:07:52.573
~ For beating the shit out of me

1:07:52.698 --> 1:07:55.576
~ I see things so clearly now

1:07:55.701 --> 1:07:57.911
~ I choose my destiny

1:07:58.036 --> 1:08:00.747
Oh, Billy, I knew you had it in ya.

1:08:01.832 --> 1:08:04.710
~ We're here to help you, Billy

1:08:04.835 --> 1:08:07.880
~ Get back in school to stay

1:08:08.005 --> 1:08:11.425
~ You gotta work real hard and stick it out

1:08:11.550 --> 1:08:14.595
~ Till graduation day

1:08:14.720 --> 1:08:17.264
~ Hey, kids, it's me

1:08:17.389 --> 1:08:20.851
~ I bet you thought that I was dead

1:08:20.976 --> 1:08:23.729
~ But when I fell over I just broke my leg

1:08:23.854 --> 1:08:26.523
~ And got a haemorrhage in my head

1:08:28.775 --> 1:08:31.570
~ There are obstacles in the way

1:08:31.695 --> 1:08:34.990
- ~ But together we shall overcome
- ~ Overcome

1:08:35.115 --> 1:08:39.828
~ Cos you can't break our spirit
and you can't kill our dream

1:08:39.953 --> 1:08:44.666
~ Do you have any more gum,
more gum, more gum, more gum?

1:08:44.791 --> 1:08:47.044
~ Do you have any more gum?

1:08:55.719 --> 1:08:58.180
Oh. Hello, kids.

1:08:58.305 --> 1:09:00.516
Mr Anderson, is that you?

1:09:00.766 --> 1:09:01.642
Oh.

1:09:01.767 --> 1:09:04.269
Yes, actually, it is.

1:09:04.394 --> 1:09:07.189
This is just... Well, this is...

1:09:08.398 --> 1:09:12.986
Normally I don't allow children to be
